title: Green Arrow 31-32 (2014) (Digital) (Nahga-Empire)
description:
This is a request by a member here.  While I am more able to provide current issues, IF I can find what you are looking for I will try and post it for you.  Nemesis43 on KAT has far more resources than I and is a better bet, but I will do what I can to help the communities.  Please message me privately for requests so as not to clutter up comment sections with unrelated material.






#31  The return of Count Vertigo! As the final shot in this war is fired from his bow, what is left of Green Arrow? "The Outsiders War" part 6.

#32  "Green Arrow: Broken" part 1! With Seattle under siege and Diggle in the grip of crime Lord Richard Dragon, the Queen Legacy must find a way to move on. But is that even possible given the violent aftermath of The Outsiders War?
